import cv2
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
 
#读取图片
src = cv2.imread('E:/apple.jpg')
src = cv2.cvtColor(src,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)

#图像缩放
result = cv2.resize(src, (200,100))
print(result.shape)

#显示图像
# cv2.imshow("original", src)
# cv2.imshow("result", result)

# #等待显示
# cv2.waitKey(0)
# cv2.destroyAllWindows()
for i in [src,result]:
    plt.imshow(i)
    plt.show()

# -*- coding:utf-8 -*-
# By：Eastmount
import cv2
import numpy as np

#读取图片
src = cv2.imread('E:/apple.jpg')
src = cv2.cvtColor(src,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)

#图像平移矩阵
M = np.float32([[1, 0, 100], [0, 1, 50]])

#获取原始图像列数和行数
rows, cols = src.shape[:2]

#图像平移
# result=cv2.warpAffine(src,M,(cols, rows))
result = cv2.warpAffine(src,M,(cols,rows))

# #显示图像
# cv2.imshow("original", src)
# cv2.imshow("result", result)

# #等待显示
# cv2.waitKey(0)
# cv2.destroyAllWindows()
for i in [src,result]:
    plt.imshow(i)
    plt.show()

图像的旋转¶

In [5]:
# -*- coding:utf-8 -*-
# By：Eastmount
import cv2
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# 读取图片
src = cv2.imread('E:/apple.jpg')
src = cv2.cvtColor(src,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)

# 源图像的高、宽 以及通道数
rows, cols, channel = src.shape

# 绕图像的中心旋转
# 函数参数：旋转中心 旋转度数 scale
M = cv2.getRotationMatrix2D((cols / 2, rows / 2), 30, 1)

# 函数参数：原始图像 旋转参数 元素图像宽高
rotated = cv2.warpAffine(src, M, (cols, rows))

# # 显示图像
# cv2.imshow("src", src)
# cv2.imshow("rotated", rotated)
for i in [src,rotated]:
    plt.imshow(i)
    plt.show()

# 等待显示
# cv2.waitKey(0)
# cv2.destroyAllWindows()

图像的翻转¶

In [11]:
import numpy as np
import cv2
from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
 
img = cv2.imread('E:/apple.jpg')
src = cv2.cvtColor(src,cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)
 
def bgr2rbg(img):
    '''
        将颜色空间从BGR转换为RBG
    '''
    return img[:,:,::-1]
 
# 水平翻转
flip_h = cv2.flip(img, 1)
# 垂直翻转
flip_v = cv2.flip(img, 0)
# 同时水平翻转与垂直翻转
flip_hv = cv2.flip(img, -1)
plt.figure(figsize=(10,8))
plt.subplot(221)
plt.title('SRC')
plt.imshow(bgr2rbg(img))
 
plt.subplot(222)
plt.title('Horizontally')
plt.imshow(bgr2rbg(flip_h))
 
plt.subplot(223)
plt.title('Vertically')
plt.imshow(bgr2rbg(flip_v))
 
plt.subplot(224)
plt.title('Horizontally & Vertically')
plt.imshow(bgr2rbg(flip_hv))
 
plt.show()
